1. *Poznajete* li se sa njim? (Do you know him?)
2. Oni se *poznaju* već godinama. (They have known each other for years.)
3. Oni su se pre nekoliko dana *poznavali*. (They were getting to know each other a few days ago.)
4. Da li ste se pre nekog *poznavali*? (Were you acquainted with someone before?)
5. Oni se još nisu *poznavali*. (They didn't know each other yet.)